snippet.title: The Thirteenth Floor - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A short horror demo in the style of the original PlayStation (PS1, PSX) made using the Unity 3D game engine

To follow progress or play the game if it's released by the time you watch this then click here: https://comp3interactive.itch.io/the-thirteenth-floor #UnityTutorial #Unity3D #Comp3interactive #GameDev
